-- Venezuela’s Sidor to Produce 3.7 Million Tons of Steel in 2012
-- B y   N a t h a n   C r o o k s
-- 2012-01-30T18:20:51Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-30/venezuela-s-sidor-to-produce-3-7-million-tons-of-steel-in-2012.html
Venezuelan state-run steel producer
Siderurgica del Orinoco expects to produce 3.7 million tons of
steel in 2012, according to an e-mailed statement from the
Information Ministry, citing Carlos D’Oliveira, president of the
steelmaker.  The majority of Sidor’s steel output will go toward a
government housing program, D’Oliveira said in the statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Nathan Crooks in Caracas at 
 ncrooks@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dale Crofts at 
 dcrofts@bloomberg.net  